00:35:40,236 --> 00:35:43,899
No. No, not at all.
I was just rereading the scripts for Monday.

536
00:35:43,973 --> 00:35:45,998
No! Off!

537
00:35:46,075 --> 00:35:48,771
What's that, Mrs. Manleigh?

538
00:35:48,844 --> 00:35:50,869
Yes. It's a good connection.

539
00:35:50,946 --> 00:35:52,937
About the script?

540
00:35:53,015 --> 00:35:57,884
Oh. Well, I'll just have to
make the revisions tonight, that's all.

541
00:35:57,953 --> 00:36:03,084
What? Oh, no, Mrs. Manleigh.
You've just got to come.

542
00:36:03,159 --> 00:36:05,184
I've looked forward
so to your meeting George...

543
00:36:05,261 --> 00:36:07,855
in line with that matter we discussed,
