546
00:36:12,635 --> 00:36:18,301
No, don't worry about that.
I always work best late at night anyway.

547
00:36:18,374 --> 00:36:20,808
Yes. 7:30.
That'll be fine.

548
00:36:20,876 --> 00:36:23,310
You can tell me about the changes
when you get here.

549
00:36:23,379 --> 00:36:25,745
Fine. Good-bye, Mrs. Manleigh.

550
00:36:25,814 --> 00:36:28,942
There's George.

551
00:36:29,018 --> 00:36:31,919
Changes, changes.
When am I supposed to sleep?

552
00:36:31,987 --> 00:36:36,390
Uh, what's, uh, Mr. Phipps gonna be
so perfect for on the radio?

553
00:36:36,458 --> 00:36:39,256
