583
00:38:13,622 --> 00:38:15,817
Nor are you expected
to pay for the scotch.

584
00:38:18,494 --> 00:38:21,554
You're quite right.
Funny how it slips my mind...

585
00:38:21,630 --> 00:38:24,428
that in certain respects,
I'm only the titular head of this house.

586
00:38:24,500 --> 00:38:27,992
Oh. Don't be silly, darling.

587
00:38:31,507 --> 00:38:33,737
I thought it very amusing
to begin with.

588
00:38:33,809 --> 00:38:36,573
Very, uh, modern and enlightened.

589
00:38:38,414 --> 00:38:40,746
