663
00:43:45,554 --> 00:43:47,545
Puratone, Sonobelle.

664
00:43:47,622 --> 00:43:49,817
<i>I thought that sounded all right.</i>
<i>Didn't you, Porter?</i>

665
00:43:49,891 --> 00:43:53,349
