You don't need a station.
Just yell a little louder.

672
00:44:09,511 --> 00:44:12,537
Uh, Mrs. Manleigh, are you sure
I can't get you a drink?

673
00:44:12,614 --> 00:44:14,946
- A cocktail maybe or scotch?
- Never touch it...

674
