This quaint situation
belongs in a true-to-life drama.

708
00:46:19,040 --> 00:46:21,873
- Are you two related?
- No, we just had the same governess.

709
00:46:21,943 --> 00:46:25,208
You kill me.

710
00:46:25,280 --> 00:46:28,807
Uh, it's just a small town. You know,
everybody gets to know everybody.

711
00:46:28,883 --> 00:46:31,408
If you don't mind
crossing the tracks.

712
00:46:31,486 --> 00:46:35,081
Oh, by the way. Sadie's quite
a radio fan. Listens all the time.

713
00:46:35,156 --> 00:46:38,751
Now, that's very interesting.
All the time, eh?

714
00:46:38,827 --> 00:46:41,318
Keep it going night and day.

715
00:46:41,396 --> 00:46:44,160
Tell me, uh, what are
