737
00:47:52,634 --> 00:47:54,966
Sorry to eat and run like this.

738
00:47:55,036 --> 00:47:57,231
So sorry.

739
00:47:57,305 --> 00:47:59,865
I won't say it doesn't matter,
because it does.

