747
00:48:29,104 --> 00:48:31,095
Just thought
I'd eat the soup while it's hot.

748
00:48:35,176 --> 00:48:37,371
George, how'd that happen?

749
00:48:37,445 --> 00:48:42,041
<i>- Baby Breath brings you</i>
