752
00:48:49,958 --> 00:48:52,825
<i>Promised a scoop</i>
<i>by her gruff city editor...</i>

753
00:48:52,894 --> 00:48:55,727
<i>Brenda Brown,</i>
<i>girl reporter for the</i> Star...

