- That's Spanish for "thank you."

761
00:49:20,288 --> 00:49:22,279
<i>Gracias.</i>

762
00:49:26,895 --> 00:49:29,329
Lord Bruce, I'm proud and flattered.

763
00:49:29,397 --> 00:49:32,594
What small-town American girl
would not be at a proposal of marriage...

764
00:49:32,667 --> 00:49:34,931
from a gentleman
as distinguished as you.

765
00:49:35,003 --> 00:49:37,028
But I must decline, with thanks.

766
00:49:37,105 --> 00:49:39,335
You decline? I don't understand.

767
00:49:39,407 --> 00:49:42,376
<i> We have Lady Bruce</i>
<i>to consider, invalid though she is...</i>

768
00:49:42,443 --> 00:49:45,378
<i>and though you've been married</i>
<i>in name only for many years...</i>

769
00:49:45,446 --> 00:49:48,506
<i>she is your wife in sickness</i>
<i>as she was in health...</i>

770
00:49:48,583 --> 00:49:50,380
<i>and must not be cast aside.</i>

771
00:49:50,451 --> 00:49:54,080
<i>- I see.</i>
<i>- Besides, I am a registered nurse.</i>

772
00:49:54,155 --> 00:49:57,056
It is my chosen professiףn,
