773
00:49:57,125 --> 00:50:01,221
<i>and much as my personal feelings</i>
<i>from time to time...</i>

774
00:50:01,296 --> 00:50:05,198
<i>You and I, my dear Lord Bruce,</i>
<i>must remain just another case...</i>

775
00:50:05,266 --> 00:50:09,430
